reviewText: My set contain the following movies.  1. His Girl Friday, 2. Penny Serenade, 3. The Man With The Golden Arm, 4. The Last Time I Saw Paris, 5. A Farewell To Arms, 6. Our Town, 7. Life With Father, 8. Love Affair, 9. A Star is Born, 10. Of Human Bondage, 11. Hometown Story (Marilyn Monroe Collection), 12. Road to Bali.

The 12 Disk Set Contains:

A Farewell to Arms

Last Time I Saw Paris

Life with Father

Our Town

Penny Serenade

Road to Bali

A Star Is Born

His Girl Friday

Love Affair

Man With Golden Arm

Of Human Bondage

My Man Godfrey

These are all available separately, but this is a great price for 12 classic movies!

I found some info on this product.  Hope it helps.  There must be more movies if the running time is 13 hours.
